: It isn't apparent there's cause here to subvert the reasonable and non-onerous autopromotion mechanism.  --[[User:Pi zero|Pi zero]] ([[User talk:Pi zero|discuss]] • [[Special:Contributions/Pi zero|contribs]]) 15:20, 20 March 2012 (UTC)
