{| class="navbox collapsible collapsed" style="text-align: left; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.2em;"
|-
! style="background:#d0e5f5; border:1px solid #abd5f5" | C source code for CPU one thread - parabolic case and GSL library  . Click on the right to view
