=== Usage ===
 <nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec= |deg= |min= |sec= |hem= }}</nowiki>

=== Examples ===

;Degrees, minutes, seconds, hemisphere
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=N}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=N}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=S}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=S}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=E}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=E}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=W}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=W}}

;Decimal degrees assigned to ''dec''
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=56.050|deg=|min=|sec=|hem=}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=56.050|deg=|min=|sec=|hem=}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=-56.050|deg=|min=|sec=|hem=}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=-56.050|deg=|min=|sec=|hem=}}

;Decimal degrees assigned to ''deg''
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=-56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=|deg=-56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}

;All fields defined
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=N}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=N}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=-56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=S}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=-56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=S}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=E}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=E}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=-56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=W}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=-56.050|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=W}}

;Parameter ''dec'' ignored when ''deg/min/sec/hem'' are defined
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=N}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=N}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=-11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=S}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=-11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=S}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=E}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=E}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=-11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=W}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=-11.070|deg=56|min=03|sec=00|hem=W}}

;Parameter ''dec'' ignored when ''deg'' is defined
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=11.070|deg=56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=11.070|deg=56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}
*<nowiki>{{Location map/decdeg|dec=-11.070|deg=-56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}</nowiki> → {{Location map/decdeg|dec=-11.070|deg=-56.050|min=|sec=|hem=}}
