{{documentation subpage}}

{{tl|precision/mini}} is very similar to {{tl|precision}}, but the output range is only 0 to 6.  Thus the functionality of {{tl|precision/mini}} is a subset of the functionality of {{tl|precision}} but the advantage is that the template code is much shorter.  It is useful when one has to be cautious of template limits.

=== Examples ===
