| <code><nowiki>{{Precision/mini|111.123456}}</nowiki></code> || {{Precision/mini|111.123456}}
|-
| <code><nowiki>{{Precision/mini|111.12345}}</nowiki></code> || {{Precision/mini|111.12345}}
